---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Chiron"
  description="Learn about Chiron and our mission to help athletes and fitness enthusiasts achieve their training goals."
>
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">
        About Chiron
      </h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-primary max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 text-center">
          Inspired by the wise centaur of Greek mythology, Chiron helps coaches and athletes shape their destinies and perform at their best. Just as legendary heroes such as Achilles, Atalanta and Heracles were guided by Chiron, we strive to provide modern coaches and athletes the insight and support needed to reach their potential.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We believe that everyone has the potential to achieve their athletic goals. Our mission is to empower athletes and coaches to train smarter, simplify the complex, and reach their performance potential.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">What We Offer</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Training Planner:</strong> Plan your training with ease. Schedule workouts and races, organise your season.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Track Progress:</strong> Automatically sync with Strava and your devices. Analyse workouts and monitor progress.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Coaching Tools:</strong> Manage athletes at scale with your workout library, training plan builder, athlete analysis, communication tools and more.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Race Timing:</strong> Run events smoothly with start lists, manual timing, RFID chip timing and instant race results.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Meet the Founder</h2>
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:items-start gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <img 
                src="/chiron-website/images/clive-gross-half-marathon-finish-4-5.jpg" 
                alt="Clive Gross - Founder of Chiron" 
                class="w-48 h-48 rounded-full object-cover bg-gray-200"
              />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Clive Gross</h3>
              <p class="text-primary-600 font-medium mb-4">Founder</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Clive is a professional engineer, family man and obsessive amateur distance runner based in Brisbane, Australia. Outside of his day job, Clive combines his passion for endurance sport, exercise physiology, technology and data science into the Chiron project.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
